text: Rosa González Román (23 July 1942 – 21 January 2019) was a Chilean journalist and politician. She was a Deputy from 11 March 1998 to 11 March 2006. She was born in Buin. González Román died in Santiago de Chile on 21 January 2019 from cervical cancer, aged 76.Fallece Rosa González, ex diputada por Arica famosa por aparición en un segundo de franja política ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Deaths from cervical cancer Category:Chilean politicians Category:Chilean writers Category:Chilean journalists
